Class UserClassLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ClassLoader

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

     class UserClassLoader
extends URLClassLoader
    An extension of URLClassLoader that keeps a list of paths in memory. Adds System.getProperty("user.dir") as default path if none are added.
